39th Avenue, adjoining the N.E. corner of Lawrence Street, showing two homes built by Walter Bogert in 1906. The houses formerly bore Nos. 12 (left) and 18 Locust Street. View 2 shows the rears of the homes, No. 12 being on the right.

Walter L. Bogert

View 1: May 19, 1910
View 2: August 18, 1915
